    Producer
    A single dedicated thread that takes MessageProducer instances from a buffer and places the messages they contain into a seperate message buffer for later consumption.
    TextfileProducer
    An implementation of the class MessageProducer, this class reads an UTF-8 file and acts as a message carrier for the different messages and icons in the text file.
